{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Automobile manufacturer\rquote s request for arbitration in action brought by dealership was \u8220\'3fembedded,\u8221\'3f for purposes of availability of immediate appeal under Federal Arbitration Act (FAA) from order compelling arbitration, inasmuch as issue of arbitrability arose in context of claim for relief by dealership that went beyond determination of dispute\rquote s arbitrability, notwithstanding that all of substantive claims in suit were would-be subjects of arbitration. 
}
