{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Order qualifies as final order within meaning of provision of Federal Arbitration Act (FAA) governing appeals if action is \u8220\'3findependent,\u8221\'3f or brought solely for purpose of obtaining such an order. 
}
